INSERT INTO accounts(role_id, email, password, phone, name, gender, address, birthday, blood_group_id, is_active)
            VALUES(
                (SELECT id FROM roles WHERE name = 'staff'),
                $1,
                $2,
                $3,
                $4,
                $5,
                $6,
                $7,
                (SELECT id FROM blood_groups WHERE name = $8),
                true
            )
            RETURNING id
